Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:01.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome has fallen into\nthe hands of Hoshiyomi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who is after the\NNaginata of Kenkon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:19.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just you wait, Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga has lost its power,\nbut I'll rescue you without fail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:10.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Hoshiyomi, huh?\NMove outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:13.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja {\i1}technique....{\i0}\NShadow Incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could the "Kagome" that was\nwritten on that scroll be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! Take the Ken blade\nand run to Furai Shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:43.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot leave you by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't you figured it out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the power you throw at me\nis being absorbed by the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This aura is from\NHoshiyomi's Kon blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're okay!\NWhere's Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}was....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome {\i1}was....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to protect the Ken blade\neven if it means this woman's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What can you kill with\na rusty sword like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}Tetsusaiga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to get her back,\ncome to Furai Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And don't forget the\NKen blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:46.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll only be in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:51.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to Lady Kaede,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Furai Shrine is the place to\npurify the Kenkon blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why did he choose that shrine\nfor the exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must be some kind of trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not the time\nto be thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is in danger because\NI involved her in my problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn right! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:19.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right! Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will now proceed\nwith the ritual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,for the resurrection of\nthe Naginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not allow them\nto get near this shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave that half-demon to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With that rusty sword,\nhe'll be no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'll take the monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tear apart the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That leaves the young\nsamurai for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get past us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You smell quite tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Seiryu of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Shippo! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you come to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've all become separated.\NHurry to Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I bruised my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shape up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh my, such nice buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, cute samurai!\NI'm Suzaku of the Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:16.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're really unlucky to have\nto face me, Genbu of the Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get outta my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what can you do\nwith a useless blade like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said to get outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Did a mosquito sting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not working, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't even need Tetsusaiga\nto fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I keep telling you\nit's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His body's so tough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja technique!\NSpinning Demon Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't hunted a\nfemale prey in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja technique,\NDance of Scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon ninja technique,\NScale Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:25.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's only if you can\nbeat me, Byakko of the Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use my Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you, Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you have\nthe Ken blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you give me the blade of Ken,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll use the skin off of your cute\nface to decorate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you be more agreeable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, every morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kiss a wall hanging\nmade from the skin of your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're disgusting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:13.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't watch this!\NIt's the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}gotta....I{\i0} gotta keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man's eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're so sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is a human like you\ntraveling with that half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you to that half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans and demons have\nno love for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:15.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There could never be a\nbond between humans and demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is because humans always\nend up betraying demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And someday, you too, will betray\nthat half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are weak creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are weak in body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though they are weak,\nthey try to live proudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why humans {\i1}betray....{\i0}\nin order to protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You misjudge humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did something happen between\nyou and humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why you say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A female samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that in the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsukiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:13.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshiyomi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin! Pyo! To! Sha! Kai! Chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Retsu! Zai!\N- Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was sealed in here by Tsukiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of the Naginata of {\i1}Kenkon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Ken blade was taken to\NMt. Fuji to the Hojo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Kon blade was\ntaken to Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Mt. Hakurei collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I took back this blade of Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's why Old Kaede said{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that the Naginata of Kenkon could be\npurified at Furai Shrine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She promised to live\nwith me, yet she betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0} Tsukiyomi must have\nhad a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are weak, yet they try to live.\NSo they struggle and betray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My desire is to save humans\nfrom that struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save humans? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will resurrect\nthe Naginata of Kenkon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which was created\nfrom the corpses of 222 demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and kill all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think that is\nsaving humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans have an existence\nthat is beyond saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So death is the only way\nto save humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I first saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt a spiritual power whose scope was\nsimilar to that of Tsukiyomi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why did I not take the\NKen blade back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but brought you here instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am going to use your power in\nthe ritual to resurrect the Naginata of Kenkon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}strength....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you yearn for it so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:42.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest assured. The other blade\nshall soon be in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki is going up\nthe waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:19.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Ninja technique,\NShell Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away {\i1}now....{\i0}\nyou half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:40.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall take good care\nof your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mi....roku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Concerned about that girl, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll soon meet in\nthe netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tiger Fang Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, I don't know what\nyou're trying to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you can't move an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! What'll happen\nif you don't keep it together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless I keep it together,\nit'll all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki! You just hang in\nthere for just a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, grab on!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away,\nmy cute samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango! Grab onto something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is {\i1}bad....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No! Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0} Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:02.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:05.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we'd better {\i1}hurry....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all right, Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Ken blade entered that {\i1}building....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}this....?{\i0}\NI got a bad {\i1}feeling....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:06.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has been restored!\NMy Naginata of Kenkon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall tell {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kenkon signifies the yin and yang.\NHeaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It represents the two opposing forces\nof the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if I were to use the power\nof the Naginata of Kenkon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to cut the invisible wall which\nseparates the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need a lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just hurry it up and\ngive Kagome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are weak.\NHumans betray.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thus, all humans must perish\nfrom this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're being sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't use the Wind Tunnel\nif he has Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Doesn't Tetsusaiga\nhave its power back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit, it's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's....It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I got Kagome involved\nin all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I let her fall\ninto his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time\nfor whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must do everything possible\nto save Kagome from that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Tetsusaiga is {\i1}still....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:56.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All you hafta do is put some spirit into it!\NAnd anything is possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:47.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will never forgive humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:49.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did Tsukiyomi seal me away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted you to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted you to remember\nthe kindness you showed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,during the days we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The power of loving {\i1}someone....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that capable of winning over
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the sadness that is enveloped\nin those terrible blades?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Eternal Love: The Naginata of Kenkon"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There has to be a dream\nthat never fades
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even if it never comes true.
